| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0326 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6fc9d700-676b-5dc5-9fd2-60c394cb6b70"
